{"id":14881881,"mediaExerciseId":"58ebda44-832c-4596-9572-21b4c9f46dc9","exerciseName":"9","chapterName":"24","chapterTitle":"Options and Corporate Finance","groupId":612499,"groupTitle":"Questions and Problems","isPremium":true,"sectionName":null,"sectionTitle":null,"pageNumber":825,"solutions":[{"id":6508813,"modifiedOn":"2021-01-01T00:00:00.000000","steps":[{"columns":[{"text":"In this exercise, we are going to learn about conversion value. ","images":{"latex":null,"additional":null},"hasInvalidKatex":false,"isTextOnly":true}],"isResult":false,"stepNumber":1},{"columns":[{"text":"To start with, let us define conversion value.\n\nThe ability of a bond to be converted into common stocks is a feature of a special type of bond. The converted amount into common stock is the **conversion value of the bond.**","images":{"latex":null,"additional":null},"hasInvalidKatex":false,"isTextOnly":false}],"isResult":false,"stepNumber":2},{"columns":[{"text":"Here are the parameters to solve the problem : \n\n|Given | | \n|--|--| \n|Par Value of Bonds |$1,000 | \n|Conversion Price |$27/share | \n|Current Price of Common Stock |$31/share | \n","images":{"latex":null,"additional":null},"hasInvalidKatex":false,"isTextOnly":false}],"isResult":false,"stepNumber":3},{"columns":[{"text":"The conversion value is solved as follows: \n\n&nbsp;\n\n$$\\begin{aligned}\n\\textbf{Conversion Value}&=\\left(\\frac{\\text{Par Value of Bond}}{\\text{Conversion Price/Share }}\\right)\\times\\text{Current price of Stock}\\\\[20pt]\n&=\\left(\\frac{\\$1,000}{\\$27}\\right)\\times\\$31\\\\[20pt]\n&=\\$37.037\\times\\$31\\\\[20pt]\n&=\\boxed{\\$1,148.15}\n\\end{aligned}$$\n\nThe ratio of the bond's par value and of conversion price per share is multiplied by the current price of the common stock to determine the bond's conversion value. \n\nThus, the conversion value is $1,148.15. \n\n","images":{"latex":null,"additional":null},"hasInvalidKatex":false,"isTextOnly":false}],"isResult":false,"stepNumber":4}],"rating":0,"solutionUuid":"168a0248-6455-4064-9b67-1eb54e946066","editorVersion":2,"answeredOn":null,"ratingCount":null,"solutionOrder":null,"totalSteps":4}],"textbook":{"authors":"Bradford D. Jordan, Randolph W. Westerfield, Stephen A. Ross","imageUrl":"https://d2nchlq0f2u6vy.cloudfront.net/textbook_covers/tmpm0p82b7h","imageThumbnailUrl":"https://d2nchlq0f2u6vy.cloudfront.net/cache/d1/d3/d1d34d106dd29dd2e71be582412ef59d.jpg","id":34320,"isbn":"9781259918957","isPremium":true,"title":"Fundamentals of Corporate Finance","edition":"12th Edition","verifiedSolutionCount":1217,"shouldBeIndexableForSeo":true,"modified":1665448474394,"active":true,"publisher":"McGraw-Hill Education","mainTextbookIsbn":null,"subjects":{"level1":["Social Science"],"level2":["Economics"],"level3":["Finance"]}},"nextExercises":[{"id":14881885,"exerciseName":"13","page":825,"hasSolution":true,"mediaExerciseId":"8246fc74-a0c7-4f8c-af63-440892c80e1f","_webUrl":"https://quizlet.com/explanations/textbook-solutions/fundamentals-of-corporate-finance-12th-edition-9781259918957/chapter-24-questions-and-problems-13-8246fc74-a0c7-4f8c-af63-440892c80e1f"},{"id":14881886,"exerciseName":"14","page":825,"hasSolution":true,"mediaExerciseId":"b5ec1560-3828-4ce0-b9de-c9d27b17c3b2","_webUrl":"https://quizlet.com/explanations/textbook-solutions/fundamentals-of-corporate-finance-12th-edition-9781259918957/chapter-24-questions-and-problems-14-b5ec1560-3828-4ce0-b9de-c9d27b17c3b2"}],"previousExercises":[{"id":14881880,"exerciseName":"8","page":825,"hasSolution":true,"mediaExerciseId":"affea83d-ef9b-4f53-bdbe-6518bd662cf9","_webUrl":"https://quizlet.com/explanations/textbook-solutions/fundamentals-of-corporate-finance-12th-edition-9781259918957/chapter-24-questions-and-problems-8-affea83d-ef9b-4f53-bdbe-6518bd662cf9"},{"id":14881879,"exerciseName":"7","page":824,"hasSolution":true,"mediaExerciseId":"2fdbb455-5ea7-47f8-973c-7b9da0dc1686","_webUrl":"https://quizlet.com/explanations/textbook-solutions/fundamentals-of-corporate-finance-12th-edition-9781259918957/chapter-24-questions-and-problems-7-2fdbb455-5ea7-47f8-973c-7b9da0dc1686"}],"_webUrl":"https://quizlet.com/explanations/textbook-solutions/fundamentals-of-corporate-finance-12th-edition-9781259918957/chapter-24-questions-and-problems-9-58ebda44-832c-4596-9572-21b4c9f46dc9"}